natspec.author: Leonardo Urrego

GetHouseUserList(address).notice: The list of all users address

SignerOCBulkVote(uint256[],bool,string,a.notice: Retrieve the signer from Offchain BulkVote signature

params._propIds: Array with ID of the proposal to votes
params._support: is the Vote (True or False) for all proposals

SignerOCInvit(bool,string,address,bytes).notice: Retrieve the signer from Offchain Invitation signature

SignerOCInvitUser(address,string,string,.notice: Retrieve the signer from Offchain Invite User signature

params._isManager: True if is for a manager
params._name: Can be the nickname or other reference to the User

SignerOCNewCLH(string,bool,bool,uint256,.notice: Retrieve the signer from Offchain New house signature

params._houseOpen: If is set to 1, the CLH is set to open
params._housePrivate: If is set to 1, the CLH is set to private
params._whiteListNFT: Address of NFT Collection for users invitation

SignerOCNewLock(uint256,uint256,uint256,.notice: Retrieve the signer from Offchain New Lock signature

params._keyPrice: Price for each lock in wei

SignerOCRequestToJoin(string,string,addr.notice: Retrieve the signer from Offchain request to join signature

params._propId: ID of the proposal, based on `arrProposals`
params._support: True for accept, false to reject
